Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙海盗哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十话 纹身的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.13,0:01:50.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感应枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:52.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神感应枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.50,0:02:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法，手竟然自己动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.50,0:02:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.70,0:02:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个打倒了水晶人的哥普拉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来事情真是不太妙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.33,0:02:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是会给主人找麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:19.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个男人就是哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.73,0:02:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.63,0:02:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和多明尼克一起死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:25.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开火！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱住我！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能拖延些时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.03,0:03:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉为何要救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开关被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.63,0:03:25.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发布进入紧急状态的通告！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.66,0:03:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以让他们两个活着离开基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.76,0:03:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为海盗的你为什么要救身为银河警察的我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我不忍看到你那可爱的屁股被机械狗咬掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.00,0:03:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那并不是真正的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:03:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底为何要救我？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是多明尼克吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:04.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.26,0:04:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是珍告诉我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你见过简了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.73,0:04:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错，还有凯萨琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.53,0:04:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她们两个在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事以后再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，你会滑雪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.83,0:04:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岂止会我要是参加奥运会的话，金牌就是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.30,0:04:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心，这是喷射滑雪器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时速能高达300公里每小时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一定很刺激的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.23,0:04:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,调校到最高速度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.53,0:05:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来我们是脱离成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.50,0:05:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心有人工暴风雪掩护我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目标！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距离480米
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正向东北方前进中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.80,0:05:46.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗？哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追兵来了吗，真快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:53.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以小看雪哥利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:06:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄得真准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.46,0:06:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们的枪装有热能感应器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是缠人的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,队长，哥普拉在这雪中好像也能看见我们
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.03,0:06:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开枪！开枪！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.73,0:06:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要让他们逃掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.90,0:06:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我能感应她们的话，就算看不到照样也能打中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们现在一定吓得不敢动了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.53,0:07:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.60,0:07:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过那家伙真固执
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.13,0:07:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:19.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说应该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看还是只有逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.43,0:07:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.56,0:07:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊，哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.66,0:07:43.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有冰裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是我们逃命的好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖跟上来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那两个白痴居然选了条绝路走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.30,0:08:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克以旗子为起点飞过去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷射滑雪器的速度无法飞过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你想被她们射成全身开遍红花吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去了，多明尼克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到她们自寻死路 省了我一番功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:35.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了不被打成马蜂窝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然选择永远埋入谷底之路
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为能打败水晶人的人\N一定是个非常厉害的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过尔尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收队！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.43,0:10:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把宇宙船藏在这种地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克就由我带走了 再见吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.00,0:10:41.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保重啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.06,0:11:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经脱离鲁鲁斯星的引力圈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.46,0:11:03.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你边查得怎么样了，哥普拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.26,0:11:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认为查得非常彻底了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是全宇宙最美丽的屁股了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不觉看呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.26,0:11:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌，你有认真的在查吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正在小心地调查中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那，有没有查出什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.03,0:11:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你们三姊妹的纹身输入电脑后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以解开其中的秘密的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:41.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！哥普拉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.76,0:11:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就告诉我两位妹妹在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍，凯萨琳与我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20年来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.80,0:12:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从未有见彼此一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.03,0:12:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说我们是亲姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.60,0:12:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是很奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳也说了同样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.76,0:12:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说的话 我很快就可以和她们见面了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:20.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.76,0:12:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍和凯萨琳现在在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.63,0:12:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.73,0:12:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.43,0:12:42.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.16,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.66,0:12:59.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.50,0:13:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍和凯萨琳，到了最后\N还是被基尔顿的海盗杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.16,0:14:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.13,0:14:11.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳和我的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:18.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会到多明尼克的姐姐那里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多明尼克！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.26,0:14:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要为妹妹她们报仇的！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要消灭基尔顿！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我看看解析内尔森船长的宝藏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想请我听音乐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的嗜好很高尚吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.40,0:15:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是能解开纹身之谜的最先进的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，今天调子不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在就开始大演奏会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了，开始解析吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.20,0:15:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:54.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍的纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.06,0:15:57.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着是凯萨琳的纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.76,0:16:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后是多明尼克你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.93,0:16:13.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果将你们三姐妹的纹身重叠在一起的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.33,0:16:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！黑成一片，什么也看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.56,0:16:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来以为三个纹身重叠的话 就会出现地图的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.73,0:16:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前方二万公里处发现敌人的电波反应
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.03,0:16:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连最先进的电脑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也解不开纹身之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太难了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那尼尔森的宝藏怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还未完全失败的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，还有这个方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快来试试
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.63,0:17:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光的三原色，红绿蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.40,0:17:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如适当混入这三原色的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论什么色彩都可以调出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.03,0:17:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说把那些纹身独自上色的话\N把它们再次重叠就会成为一张彩色照片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三人三色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细的组合就交由电脑去选
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个纹身透过选色镜着色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.26,0:17:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍是红色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.06,0:18:02.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯萨琳是绿色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.26,0:18:06.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而多明尼克你是蓝色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将这些组合合而为一的话！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.86,0:18:25.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好完美的地图！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上半部分显示了行星的坐标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下半部分则显示了宝藏所在的经度和纬度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个星球在那里？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.06,0:18:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂之星 萨德斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.26,0:18:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萨德斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔顿舰队接近中！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.40,0:18:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰约五十艘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，现在该怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.13,0:18:56.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基尔顿这么快就来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全速甩掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:18:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去萨德斯惑星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是古代宇宙文！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.43,0:19:16.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现到宇宙最终兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.36,0:19:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它放在金字塔里面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留给我的三个女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内尔森船长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.20,0:19:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终兵器？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.13,0:19:36.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到的不是财宝 居然是最终兵器！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥普拉，什么是最终兵器！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:41.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是古代火星人制造的兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:44.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说完成后它还把制造人杀了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可说是宇宙有史以来的最强兵器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:50.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙史上最强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.43,0:19:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去一直被认为这不过是个传说而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:54.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到它真的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.66,0:19:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞蒂 Formation C.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:20:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK！
